description.value:
A Chemical mined and refined from rare ores, used in many standard Imperial Explosives. It can be used to fashion crude explosives, dealing 1d10+5 X Damage per kilogram, with a radius 5x the number of kg.

Requirements

Effects are advised to taper off to prevent blowing up a planet with a few tonnes of the stuff.

Effect: Average

Notes: 70 T
